    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD model provides sufficient evidence to support the VAD hemolysis submission at the current stage. Achieved levels meet or closely approach required levels across all 13 factors. Gaps in output comparison and model form are acknowledged and bounded by the Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification. A re-validation campaign using post-revision experimental data is planned for Q2 2026 to address the stale PIV and bench characterization datasets collected prior to the January 2026 model revision; the team considers this risk acceptable given the conservative uncertainty bounds applied.",
